  "title": "Add MEMTRACE_TOKEN Environment Variable",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "The `MEMTRACE_TOKEN` environment variable is added to support `list_workspaces` and future writing tools in accessing `/api/v1/workspaces`. This variable injects the API token into the `Authorization: Bearer` header of `apiFetch`."
